name: Generated Geos
description:
You Decided To Bet Geo Coins On This New Sport Called Generated Geos! 
In This Sport Every Game It Will Place Random Geos In Random Positions! 
In This Sport You Start Of with 100 Geo Coins You Bet 20 Geo Coins On Which Team Is Going To Win If Your Team Wins You Move On And If Your Team Loses You Your Kicked Out And Lose 20 Geo Coins! 
You Can Also Draw And Move On But You Don't Get Any Geo Coins Or Lose Any Geo Coins!
The More Geo Coins You Get The Better The Team Becomes!
Every Time You Start A New Game Your Back At 100 Geo Coins!
Get The Most Geo Coins To Beat Your Highscore!
After 40S The Game Will Go Overtime And The Walls Will Close In So They Are Forced To Fight 
Highscores Do Save!
